Sweden: The Battle of Lena takes place.
Iceland: The Battle of Víðines takes place. Kolbeinn Tumason is mortally wounded.
Estonia: Sword Brothers, Letts and Livs invade Sakala and Ugandi in Southern Estonia, starting the Estonian Ancient Fight for Freedom (1208-1227).
China: Zhangzong died. He was succeeded by his brother Wanyan Yongji.
